<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Your Instructor Application | Preplings</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            background-color: #f9f9f9;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
        }
        .header {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px 0;
            border-bottom: 2px solid #f0f0f0;
        }
        .logo {
            max-width: 180px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .content {
            padding: 30px 20px;
        }
        h1 {
            color: #0D47A1;
            font-size: 24px;
            margin-top: 0;
        }
        .highlight {
            color: #0D47A1;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        .application-details {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .application-details p {
            margin: 8px 0;
        }
        .next-steps {
            background-color: #e8f4fd;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 12px 24px;
            background-color: #FFB71C;
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 6px;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-top: 15px;
        }
        .button:hover {
            background-color: #f0a700;
        }
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding-top: 20px;
            border-top: 2px solid #f0f0f0;
            color: #777;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
        .social-links {
            margin-top: 15px;
        }
        .social-links a {
            display: inline-block;
            margin: 0 8px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <img src="<%= websiteUrl %>/images/logo.png" alt="Preplings Logo" class="logo">
            <h1>Instructor Application Received</h1>
        </div>
        
        <div class="content">
            <p>Dear <span class="highlight"><%= name %></span>,</p>
            
            <p>Thank you for applying to become an instructor at Preplings! We've received your application and are excited about your interest in joining our teaching community.</p>
            
            <div class="application-details">
                <h3>Your Application Details:</h3>
                <p><strong>Name:</strong> <%= name %></p>
                <p><strong>Teaching Language:</strong> <%= language %></p>
                <p><strong>Qualification:</strong> <%= qualification %></p>
                <p><strong>Application Date:</strong> <%= applicationDate %></p>
                <p><strong>Resume:</strong> <a href="<%= resumeUrl %>" target="_blank">View your uploaded resume</a></p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="next-steps">
                <h3>What Happens Next?</h3>
                <p>Our team will review your application carefully. This process typically takes 2-5 business days. Here's what you can expect:</p>
                <ol>
                    <li>Application review by our education team</li>
                    <li>Potential interview scheduling (we'll contact you via email)</li>
                    <li>Final decision notification</li>
                </ol>
            </div>
            
            <p>If you have any questions about your application or the process, please don't hesitate to contact our support team.</p>
            
            <p>We appreciate your patience and look forward to potentially having you as part of our instructor community!</p>
            
            <a href="<%= websiteUrl %>/contact" class="button">Contact Support</a>
            
            <p>Best regards,<br>
            The Preplings Team</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="footer">
            <p>Â© <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> Preplings. All rights reserved.</p>
            <p>Our address: Language Learning Center, Education Avenue, Knowledge City</p>
            <div class="social-links">
                <a href="https://facebook.com/preplings">Facebook</a> | 
                <a href="https://twitter.com/preplings">Twitter</a> | 
                <a href="https://instagram.com/preplings">Instagram</a>
            </div>
            <p>
                <small>This email was sent to you because you submitted an instructor application on Preplings.</small>
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>